The paper focuses on designing a system that provides efficient scheduling through structured workflows, which involves human-computer interaction and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), followed by Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) since the system involves automated microtasks. The paper also mentions natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) briefly, but they are not the main focus of the paper.
